Story :
       once upon a time, there lived a Monkey who resided on a tree which was on the river side banks ,
 in the same forest there lived a Crocodile and his wife in the waters.one day , the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
 the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits . the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits , as he loved them
 as days pasted by , the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.
